oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: All for the Hall (2016)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Country Music Hall of Fame & Museum (Nashville, Tenn.); Urban, Keith, 1967-; Gill, Vince;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color window card (red, light blue, navy on white) announcing All for the Hall, a benefit for the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum, featuring Keith Urban and Vince Gill along with Luke Bryan, Florida Georgia Line, Peter Frampton, Emmylou Harris, Sam Hunt, Jason Isbell, Chris Janson, Tracy Lawrence, Maddie & Tae, and Maren Morris at the Bridgestone Arena on April 12.
